{"tid":1019792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說有冇巴絲喺西鐵俾南亞人借錢？","createTime":"2019-02-13T07:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T08:11:41.000Z","uid":44962,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96abe88984c98e025f56cdc04539ae515561c05e","tid":1019792,"uid":44962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"頭先喺屯門啱啱坐落西鐵嗰陣有個望落似南亞人嘅人搵我（佢自稱自己嚟自Tanzania) 佢話過嚟旅行嘅 不過就啱啱俾人偷曬啲行李身上面乜都冇 頭先就去完報案但因為覺得啲警察冇鬼用又扔咗張報案張 之後就問我借咗一舊水聽日拎返啲錢會還俾我 所以就留咗電話同借咗錢俾佢。 <br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲有冇遇過類似事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  感覺好似俾佢昆咗咁 似終南亞人出現喺屯元天真係最佳組合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過又覺得如果我真係幫到佢咁100蚊又唔係咩大數目啫 只係自己怕留咗電話會有麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d3081b7cef5907b6ea583e1d72fb6c5db29468","tid":1019792,"uid":195920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b5bb0706a82f935ff080e04477b1abcc5b8bda","tid":1019792,"uid":111969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"你大獲了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次出街小心啲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fe67b47371ba1a2daf62338f3b4f228b022ab4","tid":1019792,"uid":44962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b5bb0706a82f935ff080e04477b1abcc5b8bda","tid":1019792,"uid":111969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"你大獲了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次出街小心啲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:29:26.000Z","msg"